"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        QueryResponsePayload structures with different object types fields.
        """
a = payloads.QueryResponsePayload(object_types=[enums.ObjectType.
    CERTIFICATE, enums.ObjectType.SYMMETRIC_KEY, enums.ObjectType.
    PUBLIC_KEY, enums.ObjectType.PRIVATE_KEY, enums.ObjectType.TEMPLATE,
    enums.ObjectType.SECRET_DATA])
b = payloads.QueryResponsePayload(object_types=[enums.ObjectType.
    PRIVATE_KEY, enums.ObjectType.TEMPLATE, enums.ObjectType.SECRET_DATA])
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
